videos.description: Gabby Williams quickly passes it off to Kia Nurse, who drains a 3-pointer from the wing to extend the Huskies' lead over Memphis.
videos.headline: UConn's Nurse hits 3 from wing

videos.description: Gabby Williams intercepts a pass and chucks it to Megan Walker, who takes it down the court for a breakaway layup.
videos.headline: UConn's Walker goes coast to coast

videos.description: UConn head coach Geno Auriemma breaks down Gabby Williams' performance in the Huskies' 97-49 win.
videos.headline: Auriemma praises Williams in win against Memphis
